item.description:
Updated 5/17: It looks like the rain will stop by this afternoon, so we are on for today.

I'll set up a net at 1 PM.

Location: Grass fields at Sidney and Pacific Street in Cambridge.

Access by T: Central Square stop. Walk down Mass Ave towards MIT and make a right on Sidney Street. Walk down Sidney street about 4 blocks to Pacific Street. It's about a 5-10 minute walk from the T stop.

Parking: There are spots on Tudor Street between Sidney and Brookline that are free to park at on weekends.
item.name: Cambridge volleyball Sat 5/17 @ 1 PM
